    <item>
      <title>Bài 1: Javascript là gì? Viết chương trình đầu tiên</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/LapTrinhMangMayTinh/posts/post1/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/LapTrinhMangMayTinh/posts/post1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;1-hằng-trong-javascript&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  1. Hằng trong JavaScript&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#1-h%e1%ba%b1ng-trong-javascript&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Để khai báo hằng trong JavaScript chúng ta sử dụng cú pháp:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kr&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;tenHang&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;giatri&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Trong đó:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;tenHang&lt;/strong&gt;: Là tên của hằng các bạn muốn đặt.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;giatri&lt;/strong&gt;: Là giá trị của hằng, có thể là số, chuỗi, mảng, object.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chú ý:&lt;/strong&gt; Tên Hằng phải được đặt theo quy tắc sau đây:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Tên hằng bắt đầu phải là chữ cái hoặc ký tự &lt;code&gt;_&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Tên hằng không được bắt đầu bằng số.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Tên hằng có độ dài không giới hạn.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ví dụ:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bài 2: Toán tử trong Javascript</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/LapTrinhMangMayTinh/posts/post2/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/LapTrinhMangMayTinh/posts/post2/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;toán-tử-trong-javascript&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Toán tử trong JavaScript&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#to%c3%a1n-t%e1%bb%ad-trong-javascript&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Bài viết này tóm tắt các loại toán tử cơ bản trong JavaScript: toán tử gán, số học, kết hợp, quan hệ và logic, kèm ví dụ.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-toán-tử-gán&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  1. Toán tử gán&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#1-to%c3%a1n-t%e1%bb%ad-g%c3%a1n&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Toán tử gán dùng để gán giá trị cho biến. Dấu gán là &lt;code&gt;=&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Ví dụ:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;1996&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-toán-tử-số-học&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  2. Toán tử số học&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#2-to%c3%a1n-t%e1%bb%ad-s%e1%bb%91-h%e1%bb%8dc&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Các phép toán cơ bản: cộng, trừ, nhân, chia, chia lấy dư.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bài 3: Câu lệnh điều kiện trong javascript</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/LapTrinhMangMayTinh/posts/post3/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/LapTrinhMangMayTinh/posts/post3/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;1-câu-lệnh-if-trong-javascript&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  1. Câu lệnh if trong JavaScript&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#1-c%c3%a2u-l%e1%bb%87nh-if-trong-javascript&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;câu-lệnh-if&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Câu lệnh if&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#c%c3%a2u-l%e1%bb%87nh-if&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cú pháp:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;condition&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;// nếu điều kiện đúng thì thực hiện&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Trong đó &lt;strong&gt;condition&lt;/strong&gt; là một hoặc nhiều mệnh đề điều kiện có giá trị trả về &lt;strong&gt;true/false&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ví dụ:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;b&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;// Vì a khác b nên code phía trong if sẽ được chạy&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;document&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;write&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;a khác b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;câu-lệnh-else&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Câu lệnh else&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#c%c3%a2u-l%e1%bb%87nh-else&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Câu lệnh &lt;code&gt;else&lt;/code&gt; được thực thi khi điều kiện trong &lt;code&gt;if&lt;/code&gt; không thỏa mãn.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bài 4: Vòng lập trong javascript</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/LapTrinhMangMayTinh/posts/post4/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/LapTrinhMangMayTinh/posts/post4/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;vòng-lặp-trong-javascript&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Vòng lặp trong JavaScript&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#v%c3%b2ng-l%e1%ba%b7p-trong-javascript&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Một vòng lặp là chuỗi hành động được lặp đi lặp lại theo một nguyên tắc nhất định (ví dụ: sinh → lão → bệnh → tử). Trong JavaScript có các dạng vòng lặp chính: &lt;code&gt;for&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;while&lt;/code&gt;, và &lt;code&gt;do...while&lt;/code&gt; (và &lt;code&gt;forEach&lt;/code&gt;, sẽ đề cập sau).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-vòng-lặp-là-gì&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  1. Vòng lặp là gì&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#1-v%c3%b2ng-l%e1%ba%b7p-l%c3%a0-g%c3%ac&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Vòng lặp cho phép thực thi lặp một đoạn mã nhiều lần cho tới khi đạt được điều kiện dừng.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
